  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180 C and grease a 9x5 inch loaf pan.",
    "Whisk together the soy milk, almond oil, vanilla extract, and lemon zest in a bowl until combined.",
    "Sift the all-purpose flour, whole wheat flour, baking powder, salt, and cinnamon into another bowl.",
    "Pour the wet mixture into the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Fold in the crushed dates and walnuts, taking care not to overmix.",
    "Pour the batter into the prepared loaf pan and smooth the top.",
    "Bake for 45 minutes, or until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean.",
    "Remove from the oven and let the cake cool in the pan for 10 minutes before slicing.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature, optionally dusting with powdered sugar."
  ],
